General.Name: Alligator Energy Ltd
General.Description: Alligator Energy Limited engages in the mineral exploration activities in Australia and Italy. The company primarily explores for uranium, nickel, cobalt, copper, and other energy mineral deposits. It holds interests in the Alligator Rivers Uranium Project located in Northern Territory; Samphire Uranium Project South Australia and Big Lake Uranium Project situated in South Australia; and Piedmont project located in Northern Italy. The company has a strategic relationship with Traxys North America LLC to provide uranium marketing services for future uranium production, long term offtake contracting, project development financing, and assistance in uranium project acquisition opportunities. Alligator Energy Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Brisbane, Australia.
